Nexus should have item retrieval using only the canonical source Even requests for nexus metadata like "/.meta/repository-metadata.xml" are relayed to mirrors if it is not found in the main proxy.
Could be fixed by introducing an 'canonicalOnly' flag like 'local/remoteOnly'.

